*Pisac* je napisao knjigu koja je bila veliki hit. (The *writer* has written a book that was a great success.)

Neka od najboljih dela su napisana od strane *pisca*. (Some of the best works were written by the *writer*.)

Komercijalni *pisac* je nagrađen za svoj rad. (The commercial *writer* was rewarded for his work.)

Ona je *pisala* knjigu u toku prošle godine. (She was *writing* a book during last year.)

On je *pisao* pesme u svojoj mladosti. (He was *writing* songs in his youth.)

Ona je postala *pisac* u svojim tridesetim godinama. (She became a *writer* in her thirties.)